                <p>Lord Gresham, one of The FEW, commands awe and fear throughout the galaxy. With dark hair and ocean-blue eyes that turn black during intense emotions, he is a formidable figure. His all-black uniform, devoid of decoration, features the glowing emblem of The FEW, and his dark red cape mirrors his emotional state, billowing and snapping without wind.</p>
                <p>At his side, he carries a sword inscribed with ancient runes that glow ominously, capable of acting as both weapon and shield. Though not an officer, he works closely with the Galactic Alliance, who are honored by his presence. The FEW, a group so rare that many never encounter them, wield immense power, capable of manipulating the atmosphere and creating weather phenomena with ease.</p>
